- cs.DB (Databases) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of the data structure in IT infrastructure monitoring, which often involves databases. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possibility as the paper discusses the use of the data structure in monitoring IT infrastructure, which can be seen as a control system. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is a possibility as the paper discusses the use of the data structure in IT infrastructure monitoring, which often involves networking and internet architecture. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility as the paper mentions open-source implementations in various programming languages.
